3075
02:35:39.785 --> 02:35:41.645
and they're going to cost more if we wait.

3076
02:35:42.655 --> 02:35:44.605
Let's talk about what's not making it expensive.

3077
02:35:44.675 --> 02:35:47.605
It's not a fancy project. It's not building big offices.

3078
02:35:47.995 --> 02:35:49.885
It's not frills, it's not extras.

3079
02:35:50.235 --> 02:35:52.685
This committee, the committee that's made up of residents,

3080
02:35:53.005 --> 02:35:55.245
